WEBVTT

00:02.102 --> 00:04.570
        Cheers <i>is filmed</i>        
 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:04.604 --> 00:06.939
              MAN:              
 <i>If you look on your left,</i>      
     <i>you'll see the historic</i>    

00:06.973 --> 00:09.575
         <i>public garden,</i>         
 <i>which in colonial days was used</i>

00:09.609 --> 00:12.177
    as a public grazing area    
 for privately owned livestock. 

00:12.212 --> 00:15.080
     On your right are some     
  of the historic brownstones.  

00:15.115 --> 00:17.716
Oh, my God, step on it, Harry!  
He doesn't know what he's       
         talking about!         

00:17.751 --> 00:18.917
It's that                       
know-it-all mailman!            

00:18.952 --> 00:21.320
You wanna know the real...      
 I'll tell you the real story!  

00:21.354 --> 00:23.188
      The Clavins got here      
      before the pilgrims!      

